{"tid":1266522,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【回氣post】毋忘在莒 莊敬自強 戒急用忍","createTime":"2019-06-29T14:34:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-29T14:34:46.000Z","uid":125508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"6de1fc6e205330c2b42901a9e4cfaa7784a44c98","tid":1266522,"uid":125508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-29T14:34:46.000Z","msg":"深知各位連登人獲知又有烈士以死明志，大憤大悲，籌謀下一步行動。<br />\n現在我獻3句反共名言，共勉之：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">毋忘在莒</span></span>：任何時候都不忘本<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">莊敬自強</span></span>：莊重敬慎、自立自強<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">戒急用忍</span></span>：冷靜計劃，切勿心浮氣燥<br />\n現在我們又少一人，一定要齊上齊落<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong>世上只有我們是香港人<br />\n只有我們記得他們的犧牲</strong></span></span>"}]}